WEBVTT

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.280
to craft our own life stories.

00:03:01.880 --> 00:03:04.880
Soap operas teach us to push away doubt

00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:07.776
and believe in our capacity

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:10.416
for bravery, vulnerability,

00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:13.256
adaptability and resilience.

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:15.576
And most importantly, they show us

00:03:15.600 --> 00:03:18.160
it's never too late to change your story.

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:22.096
So with that, let's start
with soap opera lesson one:

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:24.096
surrender is not an option.

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:26.096
(Laughter)

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:30.696
